verge.com%2F2024%2F8%2F16 %2F24221166%2Fanker-maggo-wireless-qi2-charger-breath-of-the-wild-deal-sale&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Anker&lt;/a>; 优惠码 &lt;strong>;WSCPV22GRTOZ &lt;/strong>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;Dhzxkk&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component -data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Anker 重新设计了壁式充电器，使其不会经常从插座中掉出&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024 /8/7/24215215/anker-prime-charger-usb-c-gan-power&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;谷歌 Pixel 9 发布会还带来了全新的 45W USB-C 充电器&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/2024/8/14/24220190/google-charger-usb-c-pixel-9-price&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;有关 Qi2 无线充电的所有新闻&quot;,&quot;url &quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24134055/qi2-wireless-charging-apple-android-anker-mophie-belkin&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;TIi4dR&quot;>;与之前的型号一样，Anker 最新的充电座并不是特别华丽。这款时尚的二合一装置的顶部有一个磁性充电板，用于为兼容 MagSafe 的 iPhone 充电，底部有一个较慢的充电板，用于为一对无线充电...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href= “https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/16/24221166/anker-maggo-wireless-qi2-charger-breath-of-the-wild-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt; /p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/16/24221166/anker-maggo-wireless-qi2-charger-breath-of-the-wild-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/16/24221166/anker-maggo-wireless-qi2-charger-breath-of-the-wild-deal-sale</id><author><name>布兰登·威德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-08-16T11:08:44-04:00</published><updated> 2024-08-16T11:08:44-04:00</updated><title>再次在 iPhone 上玩《堡垒之夜》让我看到了另一个未来</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;两只手拿着 iPhone 玩《堡垒之夜》。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/2SwVpawXgbNbyeu5YDqlskqBHJw=/0x129:3068x2174/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73525760/IMG_6433.0