310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73525349/236811_WIFI_STOCK_CVirginia_3.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;NKRRH4&quot;>;AT&amp;T 和 Verizon 对 SpaceX 和 T-Mobile 即将推出的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.starlink .com/business/direct-to-cell&quot;>;直接到蜂窝&lt;/a>;卫星服务，认为 SpaceX 的实施将损害各自的移动宽带网络。 AT&amp;T 提交了敦促联邦通信委员会拒绝 SpaceX 放弃带外发射限制请求的文件 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fcc.gov/ecfs/document/1081242986780/1&quot;>; &lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fcc.gov/ecfs/document/1081205395437/1&quot;>;Verizon 本周&lt;/a>;，加入卫星公司的类似反对&lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.fcc.gov/ecfs/document/1081207358352/1&quot;>;EchoStar&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fcc.gov/ecfs/document/108130251822158/1&quot;>;Omnispace&lt;/ a>;.&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;X20DLc&quot;>;T-Mobile &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/8/25/23320722/spacex-starlink-t-mobile-satellite -internet-mobile-messaging&quot;>;2022 年宣布与 SpaceX 合作&lt;/a>;，承诺通过允许手机连接到 Starlink 卫星来消除盲区。 SpaceX 目前正在寻求将当前带外发射的功率通量密度限制提高“九倍”，以实施太空补充覆盖 (SCS)...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/2024/8/16/24221677/att-verizon-fcc-complaint-tmobile-spacex-starlink-satellite-service&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/16/24221677/att-verizon-fcc-complaint-tmobile-spacex-starlink-satellite-service" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/16/24221677/att-verizon-fcc-complaint-tmobile-spacex-starlink-satellite-service</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-08-16T08:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-08-16T08:00:00-04:00</updated><title>在将索尼 A95L 评为 2024 年最佳电视的竞赛中</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一名男子看着几台大电视，播放着明亮火焰的电影场景&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/R440xV9vCFzjgn4ewPYa5h_IDUw=/0x0:7798x5199/1310x873/cdn. vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73525339/Copy_of_MAJ_48.0.jpeg&quot; />; &l